'''白俄罗斯人民共和国拉达'''<ref>[http://www.radabnr.org/indexen.html Official website] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120704083750/http://www.radabnr.org/indexen.html |date=2012-07-04 }}</ref>（{{lang-be|Рада Беларускай Народнай Рэспублікі}}，缩写为{{lang|be|Рада БНР}}）是[[白俄罗斯人民共和国|白俄罗斯人民共和国]]的最高权力机构。从1919年开始，白俄罗斯人民共和国拉达一直处于流亡状态。目前，它已成为[[白俄罗斯|白俄罗斯]]侨民中最有影响力的政治组织。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.economist.com/node/10837957?story_id=10837957 |title=Heart of darkness: A ray of hope from Belarusian exiles |access-date=2014-12-30 |archive-date=2017-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171016174959/http://www.economist.com/node/10837957?story_id=10837957 |dead-url=no }}</ref>截至2021年，白俄罗斯人民共和国拉达是世界上是现存最古老的[[流亡政府|流亡政府]]。<ref>{{Cite news|title=The world's oldest government-in-exile is in Ottawa|first1=Tristin |last1=Hopper | date=May 26, 2021 |url=https://nationalpost.com/news/canada/the-worlds-oldest-government-in-exile-is-in-ottawa|access-date=2021-07-26|newspaper=National Post|language=en-CA}}</ref>

